      "court_date": "2025-08-13 9:00 AM",
      "matters": "PETITION FOR LETTERS OF ADMINISTRATION, Appointment Under IAEA<br>Off Calendar Aug-13-2025 Granted Per Written Order<br>MINI MINUTES: <br>Appearances: Thomas Wrobel appeared via zoom for and with Arthur Anthony Petitioner/Beneficiary (in person). <br>Fatmata Bangura for and with Tito Sandee Objector (in person).<br><br>Ms. Bangura stated that she had no objections to the granting of Mr. Anthony's petition, that she just wants to be reimburse for the funeral cost incurred, and that she will be handing over a check in open court in the amount of $6,823.26 from Ms. Sandee's employer.Ms. Bangura's  is ordered off calendar deeming it withdrawn.  <br><br>There being no objections, the Court granted the Petition for Letters of Administration. Arthur Anthony is appointed as the Administrator of the estate with full authority. Bond is set at $20,000.00. Order for the same signed in open Court. Status on close of estate is set for February 22, 2027 at 9:00 a.m., in Dept. 204. If either a petition for final distribution, or a petition for approval of report on status on administration is filed two weeks prior to the hearing date, the status hearing will go off calendar.  Isidoor Bornstein is appointed Probate Referee.   <br><br>Judge: Ross C. Moody. Clerk: A. Datt. Deputy: Singh. Not reported.<br>",
